data.description: GRANTS Available for this property, call for more information!  Welcome to this exquisite 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom townhome, a modern oasis built in 2017. This elegant residence boasts a plethora of features that cater to comfort, style, and entertainment, making it the perfect place to call home.  Upon arrival, you'll be greeted by the convenience of a two-car garage, offering ample parking space for both residents and guests. As you step inside, you'll find a tastefully finished basement that holds the potential to add an additional bathroom thanks to the existing rough-in plumbing. This flexible space can serve as a media room, home gym, or a versatile bonus room to suit your specific needs.  The heart of this home is undoubtedly the master suite, which offers a tranquil retreat after a long day. You'll appreciate the spacious stand-up shower for a quick, invigorating start to your day, and for those moments when you need some pampering, a luxurious jacuzzi tub is right at your disposal.  But the appeal of this townhome doesn't stop at its doorstep; it extends to the community itself. The neighborhood features a clubhouse with a conference center, providing a perfect space for social gatherings, meetings, or events. For those seeking outdoor recreation, the community boasts an Olympic-sized pool for a refreshing swim or leisurely sunbathing.  Families with children will love the multiple playground areas where kids can safely play and make friends. For the sports enthusiasts, there are facilities galore, including tennis courts, basketball courts, volleyball courts, soccer fields, and a baseball diamond. Whether you're looking for a friendly pickup game or a more serious sports practice, you'll find the perfect setting within your own community.  The rear deck of this townhome offers a peaceful view of the community pond and a winding walking trail. It's the perfect spot for watching the sunrise and sunset, allowing you to enjoy the serene beauty of nature right from the comfort of your own home.  Don't miss out on the chance to make this property your own and enjoy the abundant features it has to offer.
